Description: Provides tools to download and extract data from the 'OzButterflies' Database <https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.19019034>, 
    which contains reflectance spectra, calibrated photographs, and cytochrome c oxidase subunit I (COI) sequences of 
    Australian butterflies. The main function get_Oz_butterflies() downloads the database 
    and extracts selected files to a specified directory using user-defined filters.
